<p><strong>1、业内专家：生鲜之争是供应链之争</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200908/06cca1fa55d6433a82f7c02c925b75ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
